      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "COMMAND OPTION"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "The OS COMMAND Processor option allows operating system commands to be"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "executed from SPF/PC. The Command Processor panel is displayed when"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "option 6 is entered on the primary option panel."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Option 6 allows you to enter long commands that continue to the"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "next two lines.  A secondary command processor may be invoked by"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "specifying its name (usually CMD or COMMAND.COM).  In this event,"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "return to SPF/PC by typing EXIT from the secondary command processor"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "prompt."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Also, SPF/PC allows operating system commands to be entered in the"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "COMMAND/OPTION field of any panel."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "COMMAND +DOS DIR *.COB"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
